title: Wang Chung - City of the Angels (Big Papi Single).mp3
description:
Thanks for grabbing this. Crank it up and let's see what that stereo can do. Wang Chung is an under-recognized musical genius. Among other thing, he wrote this track for the hit 80's movie To Live and Die in L.A. This scene was when Willen DaFoe was making counterfeit money in his desert printing shop.
